# 止蝕  
(pos:動詞)  
<explanation>  
yue:投資或交易時，為咗防止損失進一步擴大而主動沽出資產，令虧損「停低」嘅行為（常見於股票、期貨、外匯等交易場合）；「蝕」指虧本，「止」即停止  
eng:to cut losses (e.g. by selling an asset to prevent further losses in trading/investment)  

<eg>  
yue:呢隻股票跌到咁犀利，再唔止蝕，下個月就要蝕晒所有本金！ (ni1 zi2 gau1 pip3 dik1 dou3 si3 lei6, zoi3 m4 zi2 sik1, haa6 go3 jyu6 jyu5 sik1 so31 bun1 cyun2!)  
eng:This stock’s falling so badly—if I don’t cut my losses now, I’ll lose all my principal next month!

yue:老細話，見到虧蝕超過一成，就要即刻止蝕，唔好心軟。 (lou5 sai3 waa6, gin3 dou3 wai6 sik1 si3 gwo3 zit1 sing1, jau4 jyu5 zap6 hak1 zi2 sik1, m4 hou6 sam1 jyun2.)  
eng:Boss said: once losses exceed 10%, you must cut them immediately—don’t be soft-hearted.

yue:佢係用止蝕點子，先至冇被套牢。 (keoi5 hai6 jyun6 zi2 sik1 dim2 zi2, sin1 zi3 mou5 bak1 tou3 lou4.)  
eng:He used a stop-loss strategy, so he wasn’t stuck in a losing position. [end of text]


